title: ProtocolLib加载失败
author: FireworkPolymer
txt_content:
本帖最后由 FireworkDLC 于 2020-3-26 17:14 编辑 

服务器版本1.12.2spigot，protocollib版本4.5.0,用的plugman。下面是详细报错信息Error Cannot load ProtocolLib. (java.lang.LinkageError: loader constraint violation in interface itable initialization: when resolving method "com.comphenix.protocol.injector.PacketFilterManager.getAsynchronousManager()Lcom/comphenix/protocol/AsynchronousManager;" the class loader (instance of org/bukkit/plugin/java/PluginClassLoader) of the current class, com/comphenix/protocol/injectorFilterManager, and the class loader (instance of org/bukkit/plugin/java/PluginClassLoader) for interface com/comphenix/protocol/ProtocolManager have different Class objects for the type com/comphenix/protocol/AsynchronousManager used in the signature) occured in ProtocolLib v4.5.0.
Error Cannot enable ProtocolLib. (java.lang.LinkageError: loader constraint violation: when resolving method "com.comphenix.protocol.PacketType.fromCurrent(Lcom/comphenix/protocolType$Protocol;Lcom/comphenix/protocolType$Sender;ILjava/lang/Class;)Lcom/comphenix/protocolType;" the class loader (instance of org/bukkit/plugin/java/PluginClassLoader) of the current class, com/comphenix/protocol/injector/netty/NettyProtocolRegistry, and the class loader (instance of org/bukkit/plugin/java/PluginClassLoader) for the method's defining class, com/comphenix/protocolType, have different Class objects for the type com/comphenix/protocolType$Protocol used in the signature) occured in ProtocolLib v4.5.0.

replies.author: xmdhs
replies.txt_content: 重启服务器来载入插件
